title: Your Second Brain
itunes:title: Your Second Brain
description:
Episode 144 - Did you know you have a part of your body that scientists call your "second brain"? Well you do, it's your gut. It holds over 100 million neurons and that is why you get a "gut feeling." In this episode I talk about trusting your gut over your brain and tell you how to use it making tough decisions.
